{"title":"有志气的好孩子","authors":["金近"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有志气的好孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长得要比爸爸高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我长高啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真的，你瞧瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年坐火车要免费，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年可以买半票。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的长裤子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越穿越短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的大棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越穿越小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈说：“哈呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你长得好快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来你长大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就高得像爸爸。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：“妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在我还小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等将来长大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要比爸爸高。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸说：“孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听了真快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可你长大了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打算干什么？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：“爸爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里老在想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像你一样报告天气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可要比你强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你只能报告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下雨起风暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只报告晴天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者云多云少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我那时候不这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造一座新的气象站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把机器一扳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要天晴就出太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是哪儿天旱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就开下雨的机关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人夏天要滑冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把河水冻得像石板。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸听我讲完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍拍我的肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“孩子啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这倒是个很好的理想。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像解放军叔叔那样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛有个志愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大起来要当解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他知道在这地球上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有最凶恶的敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那敌人就是美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像只饿狼往山下跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要不带枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会把你咬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛的年纪还小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有些事儿不知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学解放军叔叔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该怎样做才好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈告诉他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化要学好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体练得棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助别人也重要。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是算术没学好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就不会开大炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人在东边的山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却打到南边的目标。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是身体没练好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘦瘦的像只鹭鶿鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一听到自己的冲锋号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么跟敌人拼刺刀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是只顾到自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人有困难你不管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家见了都要说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这个人我可不喜欢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛都记在心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天起身得很早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像解放军叔叔那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己练习做早操。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功课争取得5分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师讲话用心听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像解放军叔叔那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读书写字挺认真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人要把小同学欺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛怎么也不同意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像解放军叔叔那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同学们就是亲兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛天天这样学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真像解放军叔叔那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他做功课总是打胜仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红5分就是他的奖章。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}